{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "campaign-reward-api-v3",
    "name": "Campaign Reward API",
    "description": "Campaign management (CRUD) + client-side booth scanning + raffle QR + spin wheel + claim flow.\n\n**Participant happy path:**\n1. `GET /campaigns/event/:eventTag` — load active campaign + active booth list\n2. Client scans booths locally (no API call per scan) → accumulates points\n3. `POST /campaigns/:campaignId/generate-raffle-qr` — submit scanned booth codes + optional participant info → receive encrypted QR\n4. Client presents QR at raffle station\n5. `POST /campaigns/:campaignId/validate-raffle` — station scans QR → creates participant record + scan logs + raffle entry atomically → returns `raffleEntryId`\n6. Wheel spins **client-side** → client sends outcome to server\n7. `POST /campaigns/:campaignId/spin-wheel` — record prize result\n\n**Note:** `GET /campaigns/:campaignId/prizes` is an **admin/stats** endpoint — it shows claim history, not a prize catalog.\n\n**Seeded campaign ID:** `1`\n**Seeded event tag:** `WORLDBEX2026`\n**Active booth codes:** BOOTH-MAIN-01 (100pts), BOOTH-TECH-01 (75pts), BOOTH-FOOD-01 (50pts), BOOTH-INNO-01 (75pts), BOOTH-SPON-01 (50pts)\n**Threshold:** 300 pts — scanning all 5 active booths gives 350 pts",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1/raffles",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "campaignId",
      "value": "1",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Auto-filled from Create Campaign or Get Campaign by Event Tag"
    },
    {
      "key": "eventTag",
      "value": "WORLDBEX2026",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "participantId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Auto-filled from Validate Raffle"
    },
    {
      "key": "raffleEntryId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Auto-filled from Validate Raffle"
    },
    {
      "key": "encryptedQr",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Auto-filled from Generate Raffle QR"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
